{"tid":233537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北 韓 再 拘 留 一 名 美 國 公 民","createTime":"2017-05-07T15:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T15:47:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23b4845efaf2f7e19d63e9655da449e3b059ca30","tid":233537,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】北韓再拘留一名美國公民，指他涉嫌從事反北韓的敵對行為。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社證實，周六被捕的男子譯名叫金學松，在平壤科技大學工作，是北韓近年來扣押的第四名美國公民。當局指他涉嫌從事敵對活動，相關機構正調查他涉及的罪行。<br />\n<br />\n另一名韓裔美國公民，亦被指涉嫌從事顛覆國家政權的敵意行為，在上月被捕。該名男子亦曾經獲邀到平壤科技大學授課，並參與援助北韓計劃。<br />\n<br />\n之前亦分別有一名韓裔牧師和一名美國學生遭北韓拘捕，兩人去年分別被判處10年和15年勞改。"},{"pid":"c5a77e1015ee461f4b3ea4e3bee30ce06ecd6940","tid":233537,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=220300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D220300&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=90f9ce01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D220300&h=6d950eca\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=220300</a>"},{"pid":"e0408f03260b081a9d1d332b3246d4e5a5dfd061","tid":233537,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢仲唔走係咩心態"},{"pid":"d28e4b78e18c1fa124d9ed6d1f497be411d3051b","tid":233537,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67ad7aa6d50c0821f5325c3a4132012220836ad","tid":233537,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"